    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Integration Points\n\n**HEBELING OS \u2192 n8n**\nWebhook trigger with manuscript metadata\n\n**n8n \u2192 Supabase**\n- Project creation\n- File storage\n- Stage tracking\n\n**n8n \u2192 Notifications**\n- Slack (team)\n- Gmail (author)\n\n**Response \u2192 HEBELING OS**\nProject ID + tracking URL",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 340,
        "color": 3
