      {
        "parameters": {
          "content": "## REINO EDITORIAL AI ENGINE\n### WF-01: Manuscript Intake Workflow\n\n**Purpose:** Receive manuscripts from HEBELING OS, validate file types, store in Supabase, and initialize editorial projects.\n\n**Trigger:** Webhook from HEBELING OS client portal\n\n**Process Flow:**\n1. Receive manuscript metadata + file URL\n2. Validate file type (DOCX, PDF, TXT, MD)\n3. Download and extract text content\n4. Create project record in Supabase\n5. Store file in Supabase Storage\n6. Initialize workflow stage tracking\n7. Notify team via Slack\n8. Send confirmation email to author\n9. Respond to HEBELING OS with project ID\n\n**Next Workflow:** WF-03 Content Extraction",
          "height": 380,
          "width": 600,
          "color": 2
        },
        "id": "629f928c-3ef2-4d38-8ec0-d183401d86d1",
        "name": "Sticky Note d9232a93",
        "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
        "typeVersion": 1,
        "position": [
          128,
          608
        ]
      },
      {
        "parameters": {
          "content": "## Database Tables Used\n\n**editorial_projects**\n- Stores project metadata\n- Tracks workflow stage\n- Progress percentage\n\n**editorial_workflow_stages**\n- Stage completion tracking\n- Timestamps for each stage\n\n**editorial_audit_logs**\n- Error logging\n- System events",
          "height": 280,
          "width": 300,
          "color": 4
        },
        "id": "82c39a21-bcd5-4e86-989a-6867aea996dd",
        "name": "Sticky Note a0c53e8e",
